To check if the app is running in the foreground, use the following code:   

```
public static boolean isForeground(Context context, String myPackage){
    ActivityManager manager = (ActivityManager) context.getSystemService(ACTIVITY_SERVICE);
    List&lt; ActivityManager.RunningTaskInfo &gt; runningTaskInfo = manager.getRunningTasks(1); 

    ComponentName componentInfo = runningTaskInfo.get(0).topActivity;
    if(componentInfo.getPackageName().equals(myPackage)) {
        return true;
    }       
    return false;
}
```
